BONUS WORD OF THE DAY: deride  \dih-RYD\  (transitive verb)

: To laugh at with contempt; to subject to ridicule or make 
sport of; to mock; to scoff at. 



                  OBSCURE AND UNUSUAL WORDS
                  *************************

	1) abbozzo  \o-bot'so\  (noun)
	   : a rough draft or sketch

	2) biunial  \bi-u'ni-el\  (adjective)
	   : combining two in one


